OL,3,CBoy, 16, fled police and caused crash
OL,4,Cwhich left woman with brain bleed
OL,6,FA teenager has been jailed after drug-
OL,7,Fdriving and crashing into another car,
OL,8,Fleaving a woman with several fractures
OL,9,Fand a bleed on the brain.
OL,11,FJames Forrest-Hazell was just 16 years
OL,12,Fold when the crash happened in
OL,13,FExmouth, in April 2023. He has since
OL,14,Fturned 18.
OL,16,FOn the day of the crash, an unmarked
OL,17,Fpolice car was responding to an
OL,18,Funrelated police incident in Exmouth
OL,19,Fwith its emergency lights on.
