OL,3,CBoy, 16, fled police and caused crash
OL,4,Cwhich left woman with brain bleed
OL,6,FThe officer recognised Forrest-
OL,7,FHazell's Ford Fiesta due to a previous
OL,8,F'fail to stop' - and saw him speeding
OL,9,Fup as they approached.
OL,11,FThe police officer followed the Fiesta
OL,12,Fand saw it overtake other vehicles in
OL,13,Fa hash marked area while driving well
OL,14,Fin excess of the 30mph limit.
OL,16,FForrest-Hazell then entered a sweeping
OL,17,Fright bend and mounted a grass verge
OL,18,Fas he lost control. His vehicle
OL,19,Fcollided with a Fiat 500, pushing it
OL,20,Fup into the air.
