OL,3,CBoy, 16, fled police and caused crash
OL,4,Cwhich left woman with brain bleed
OL,6,FAs a result of the collision, the
OL,7,Fdriver of the Fiat suffered several
OL,8,Ffractures and a bleed on the brain.
OL,10,FDevon and Cornwall Police says the
OL,11,Fcollision continues to have an effect
OL,12,Fon her to this day.
OL,14,FThe driver's son also sustained a two-
OL,15,Finch cut to his ear which needed
OL,16,Fstitches.
OL,18,FIn an interview Forrest-Hazell told
OL,19,Fofficers he panicked and accelerated
OL,20,Fwhen he saw blue lights come up behind
OL,21,Fhim.
