OL,3,CBoy, 16, fled police and caused crash
OL,4,Cwhich left woman with brain bleed
OL,6,F"In an attempt to flee from police his
OL,7,Fdriving was dangerous. Not only did he
OL,8,Fdrive at highly inappropriate speeds,
OL,9,Fbut he also overtook other cars in a
OL,10,Fresidential area of Exmouth.
OL,12,F"His reckless actions not only
OL,13,Fdiverted an officer from responding to
OL,14,Fan emergency call, but ultimately led
OL,15,Fto him seriously injuring an innocent
OL,16,Fmember of the public."
